Class SimEventResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • simj.SimEvent
      • simj.SimEventResource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimEventEndService, SimEventStartService

    public abstract class SimEventResource
extends SimEvent
    This class implements the generic concept of a discrete event associated with the request or the relinquish of a resource by a temporary entity. The execute feature depends on the specific event.
    Author:
    Patrik Fuhrer
